{"tid":1194754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(9/6)反送中","createTime":"2019-06-09T11:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T12:12:33.000Z","uid":140482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0291ca8ca2e5c5e6c76e2a48c99d2e4d602261","tid":1194754,"uid":140482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"我係人群之中<br />\n我用八達通入閘<br />\n因為我知香港仲有公義 仲有法治<br />\n我唔怕畀佢知我有參與<br />\n<br />\n林奠我唔鍾意<br />\n但呢次原意係反送中？<br />\n我聽到嗌林奠 下台<br />\n佢下左台 中央仍然可以再點人<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油 撐住 <br />\n我地有國際支持<br />\n我地唔係孤軍作戰<br />\n至少呢條街度已經有幾百萬人"},{"pid":"79653d968f1e368b9fa00c22a6258de684b0e199","tid":1194754,"uid":140482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T11:55:48.000Z","msg":"大家要記住初心<br />\n一開始好簡單 就係反送中<br />\n唔想大家想守護香港既心 變成一啲組織既武器<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"beb66e9409ec507b0b2f5598ef282a4ae4b99df4","tid":1194754,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"目仲有好多人行緊？？"},{"pid":"2af8e9f4cd3b21250ba7fe82419064cbc81c3330","tid":1194754,"uid":140482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb66e9409ec507b0b2f5598ef282a4ae4b99df4","tid":1194754,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"目仲有好多人行緊？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"係！好多！"},{"pid":"b66e10e3c00672e14b6ad9fcbb6648ef7a03807b","tid":1194754,"uid":140482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb66e9409ec507b0b2f5598ef282a4ae4b99df4","tid":1194754,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"目仲有好多人行緊？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"你都快啲黎！唔好諗多一個唔多！<br />\n唔好諗話行街有咩用<br />\n如果最基本既野都做唔好<br />\n講咩之後有咩行動"}]}